                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The subject of possible Spanish inclusion in <gloss target="#t_NAT1">NATO</gloss>
                    was raised on several occasions during the Seventh Session of the North Atlantic
                    Council at Ottawa, September 16–21, 1951. For documentation, see <ref
                        target="frus1951v03p1#pg_616">volume III, Part 1, pages 616</ref> ff.</p>
            </div>
